<codeline lineno="48"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>graph.add_node(&amp;node2);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="49"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="50"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>//<sp/>Create<sp/>and<sp/>add<sp/>an<sp/>edge<sp/>to<sp/>the<sp/>graph</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="51"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>Edge<sp/>edge(&amp;node1,<sp/>&amp;node2);</highlight></codeline>
